== Overview ==

A podcast aggregator / player written in Python / [http://trac.enlightenment.org/e/wiki/Elementary Elementary].

====Features====
* Designed to be finger friendly, fast and easy to use
* RSS, Atom feeds
* User interface in Elementary
* Auto-suspend is disabled during playing
* Playing is stopped on incoming GSM call
* Bluetooth A2DP support
* Import from OPML file

The Project is hosted on [http://code.google.com/p/podboy/ Google code].

== Download and installation ==
You can install Podboy directly from Web with opkg. All packages are available [http://code.google.com/p/podboy/downloads/list here].
For example:
<pre>
opkg install http://podboy.googlecode.com/files/podboy_1.3.5-r0_all.ipk
</pre>
Podboy is in SHR feeds already, so to install Podboy on SHR, simply type:
<pre>
opkg install podboy
</pre>

